==制作==
2017年5月，曾执导《[[飓风营救|飓风营救]]》首部的导演皮埃尔·莫瑞尔接触该项目，剧本由曾参与[[杰拉德·巴特勒|杰拉德·巴特勒]]主演电影《[[伦敦陷落|伦敦陷落]]》编剧的查德·圣约翰负责<ref>{{cite web |last=Ford |first=Rebecca |title=Cannes: Lionsgate Takes Female Action Movie 'Peppermint' |date=2017-05-21 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/cannes-lionsgate-takes-female-action-movie-peppermint-1005966 |access-date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2018-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328165552/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/cannes-lionsgate-takes-female-action-movie-peppermint-1005966 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年8月，[[珍妮佛·嘉納|珍妮佛·嘉納]]就加盟剧组事宜进行商讨<ref>{{cite web |last=Lee |first=Ashley |title=Jennifer Garner in Talks to Star in Revenge Thriller 'Peppermint' |date=2017-08-08 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/peppermint-jennifer-garner-talks-star-revenge-thriller-1027632 |access-date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2018-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328171204/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/peppermint-jennifer-garner-talks-star-revenge-thriller-1027632 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Mike Fleming Jr. |title=Jennifer Garner Joins Lakeshore & Pierre Morel-Helmed Revenge Thriller 'Peppermint'; STX films To Distribute |date=2017-08-08 |work=Deadline Hollywood |url=https://deadline.com/2017/08/jennifer-garner-peppermint-revenge-thriller-stx-entertainment-lakeshore-pierre-morel-1202143910/ |access-date=2017-03-28 |archive-date=2017-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808172441/http://deadline.com/2017/08/jennifer-garner-peppermint-revenge-thriller-stx-entertainment-lakeshore-pierre-morel-1202143910/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

影片于加利福尼亚取景，历时50天<ref name="CFC" />。

特技协调员唐李（Don Lee）曾与嘉納在《[[夜魔俠_(電影)|夜魔俠]]》和《[[黑天使_ELEKTRA|黑天使 ELEKTRA]]》中有过合作<ref>{{cite web |author1=Brittany Frederick |title=Peppermint interview: Don Lee on coordinating Jennifer Garner’s fights |url=https://fansided.com/2018/12/15/peppermint-don-lee-jennifer-garner-fight-coordinator/ |website=FanSided |date=2018-12-15 |accessdate=2020-11-12 |archive-date=2018-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216125425/https://fansided.com/2018/12/15/peppermint-don-lee-jennifer-garner-fight-coordinator/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。嘉纳为影片的戏份接受为期三个月的培训，包括舞蹈、有氧运动、举重、拳击、枪械，以及和长期合作的替身肖娜·杜金斯（Shauna Duggins）就特级工作进行配合<ref>{{cite web | date = 2018-09-07 | author = Ruth Kinane | title = Jennifer Garner had 'the greatest fun' training to kick butts for 'Peppermint' | url = https://ew.com/movies/2018/09/07/jennifer-garner-peppermint-interview/ | website = Entertainment Weekly | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archive-date = 2020-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200916100530/https://ew.com/movies/2018/09/07/jennifer-garner-peppermint-interview/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=2018-08-20 |author=Amy Nicholson |title=Jennifer Garner Talks Walk of Fame, TV After ‘Alias’ |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/features/jennifer-garner-walk-of-fame-alias-1202903262/ |website=Variety |quote=I don’t like to give up my action scenes to my beloved double Shauna [Duggins] to do for me because I want to do them |accessdate=2020-11-12 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106185438/https://variety.com/2018/film/features/jennifer-garner-walk-of-fame-alias-1202903262/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

