影片于洛杉矶富豪院线现场秀14号体育馆（Regal Cinemas L.A. LIVE Stadium 14）首映<ref name="Quinn">{{cite web |date=2018-08-29 |author=Dave Quinn |title=Jennifer Garner Returns to the Red Carpet in a Little Black Dress at Peppermint Premiere |url=https://people.com/style/jennifer-garner-peppermint-premiere-little-black-dress/ |website=PEOPLE.com |accessdate=2020-11-12 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109004844/https://people.com/style/jennifer-garner-peppermint-premiere-little-black-dress/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主演嘉纳在影片发行当天入主[[好莱坞星光大道|好莱坞星光大道]]<ref>{{cite web |date= 2018-08-21 |last1= Delbyck |first1= Cole |title= Jennifer Garner Makes Rare Appearance With Kids At Hollywood Walk Of Fame Ceremony |url= https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/jennifer-garner-kids-hollywood-walk-of-fame-ceremony_us_5b7b644de4b0a5b1febe2cd0 |website=Huffington Post |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181127173657/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/jennifer-garner-kids-hollywood-walk-of-fame-ceremony_us_5b7b644de4b0a5b1febe2cd0 |archive-date= 2018-11-27 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

影片于2018年9月7日在美国公映<ref>{{cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |title=Jennifer Garner Thriller 'Peppermint' Sets Post-Labor Day Weekend Debut |date=2018-03-22 |work=Deadline Hollywood |url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/jennifer-garner-peppermint-stx-movie-release-date-1202351532/ |access-date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2018-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327211938/http://deadline.com/2018/03/jennifer-garner-peppermint-stx-movie-release-date-1202351532/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=variety>{{cite web |last=McNary |first=Dave |title=Jennifer Garner's Action-Thriller 'Peppermint' Sets September Release |date=2018-03-22 |work=Variety |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/jennifer-garner-thriller-peppermint-september-1202733627/ |access-date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2018-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328231058/http://variety.com/2018/film/news/jennifer-garner-thriller-peppermint-september-1202733627/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=N'Duka |first=Amanda |title='Taken' Helmer Pierre Morel To Direct 'The New Mrs. Keller' With Claes Bang Set As Lead |date=2018-03-22 |work=Deadline Hollywood |url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/pierre-morel-direct-the-new-mrs-keller-claes-bang-1202351588/ |access-date=2018-03-28 |archive-date=2018-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180328165602/http://deadline.com/2018/03/pierre-morel-direct-the-new-mrs-keller-claes-bang-1202351588/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
影片北美票房3540万美元，海外1840万美元，全球合计5380万美元<ref name="BOM">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=peppermint.htm|title=Peppermint (2018)|website=Box Office Mojo|access-date=2019-06-28|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402192651/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=peppermint.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收回2280万至2500万美元的制片成本<ref name="CFC">{{cite report |title= Film and Television Tax Credit Program Program 2.0 |url= http://film.ca.gov/wp-content/uploads/CFC-Approved-Projects-List.pdf |publisher= California Film Commission |page= 9 |access-date= 2019-09-09 |date=  |archive-date= 2017-10-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171004180757/http://film.ca.gov/wp-content/uploads/CFC-Approved-Projects-List.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="BOM" />。

北美方面，影片与《[[鬼修女|鬼修女]]》和《{{le|上帝保佑坎坷的旅途|God Bless the Broken Road}}》同期上映，首周末在2980家影院上映，预计影片在1000万至1300万美元之间<ref name="BOpreview">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/09/the-nun-box-office-projection-jennifer-garner-peppermint-1202456596/ |title='The Nun' To Fly To $40M+, Eyes Record Opening For 'Conjuring' Franchise – Box Office Preview |website=Deadline Hollywood |date=2018-09-04 |first=Anthony |last=D'Alessandro |access-date=2018-09-04 |archive-date=2018-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904230105/https://deadline.com/2018/09/the-nun-box-office-projection-jennifer-garner-peppermint-1202456596/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首日票房470万美元，含周四晚点映的80万。其后以1340万美元的成绩空降票房榜第二位，仅次于《鬼修女》<ref name="opening">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/09/the-nun-weekend-box-office-conjuring-records-peppermint-jennifer-garner-1202459068/ |title='The Nun' Hits The Hallelujah With $54M Opening, Best Ever In 'Conjuring' Universe – Sunday AM Update |website=Deadline |date=2018-09-09 |first=Anthony |last=D'Alessandro |access-date=2018-09-09 |archive-date=2019-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829180028/https://deadline.com/2018/09/the-nun-weekend-box-office-conjuring-records-peppermint-jennifer-garner-1202459068/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===专业评价===
[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据142条评论打出12%的腐烂度，平均得分3.49/10。网站共识写道：“《薄荷》浪费了珍妮佛·嘉纳的杰出表现，讲述了沉闷的死刑复仇故事，缺乏独特的反转或扣人心弦的刺激感，并没有那么地让人觉得耳目一新<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/peppermint_2018 |title=Peppermint (2018) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |access-date=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116210405/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/peppermint_2018 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]评论26条，加权平均分29/100，表示“普遍差评”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/peppermint |title=Peppermint reviews |website=Metacritic |access-date=2018-09-20 |archive-date=2018-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180920080507/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/peppermint |dead-url=no }}</ref>。从A+到F，[[影院评分|影院评分]]观众评分为B+<ref name="opening" />。

《[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]》的弗兰克·施切克（Frank Scheck）认为影片是“打满类固醇的《{{tsl|en|Death Wish (film series)|虎胆追凶电影系列|虎胆追凶}}》”，“缺乏细微之处，甚至远远谈不上令人信服。但就和它的女主角一样，影片拍的确实很完整”<ref>{{cite web |first=Frank |last=Scheck |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/peppermint-review-1140251 |title='Peppermint' Review |work=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=2018-09-13 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906234630/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/peppermint-review-1140251 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]裘德·德赖（Jude Dry）给出“C+”的评分，认为影片“罕见回归到适合嘉纳的模式中，让嘉纳毫不费力地用魅力呈现她的私刑争议”，但不幸的是，“这也是观看《薄荷》的唯一原因”，认为嘉纳应该参加更出色的电影<ref>{{cite web |first=Jude |last=Dry |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/09/peppermint-review-jennifer-garner-1202001051/ |title='Peppermint' Review: Jennifer Garner's Vigilante Mom Deserves Better |website=IndieWire |date=2018-09-06 |access-date=2018-09-13 |archive-date=2018-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907125417/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/09/peppermint-review-jennifer-garner-1202001051/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的{{tsl|en|Richard Roeper|理查德·罗珀}}打出2/4星，认为“在导演表现时尚但令人生厌、陈词滥调满溢的《薄荷》中，嘉纳饰演了两个从一个模子里分出来的两种角色”<ref>{{cite web |first=Richard |last=Roeper |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/peppermint-review-movie-jennifer-garner-film/ |title='Peppermint' movie review: Jennifer Garner back to kicking butt in nasty revenge thriller |work=Chicago Sun-Times |date=2018-09-06 |access-date=2018-09-13 |archive-date=2018-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907125631/https://chicago.suntimes.com/entertainment/peppermint-review-movie-jennifer-garner-film/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]》的托德·吉尔克里斯特（Todd Gilchrist）认为：“《薄荷》最终留下的是老套桥段，犹如藏在钱包底部的未包装糖果”<ref>{{cite web |last=Verhoeven |first=Beatrice |url=https://www.thewrap.com/peppermint-film-review-jennifer-garner/ |title='Peppermint' Film Review: Jennifer Garner Vengeance Saga Lacks Snap |website=The Wrap |access-date=2018-09-13 |archive-date=2018-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907150528/https://www.thewrap.com/peppermint-film-review-jennifer-garner/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的安德鲁·贝克（Andrew Barker）写道：“嘉纳得到了她所要求的一切，从暴虐的躯体到润饰眼眸的柔情，但这种愚钝的灾难几乎破坏了其他一切。这种情况非常突出，直到突然消失，可以说《薄荷》从头到尾都失火了<ref>{{cite web |date= 2018-09-06 |first= Andrew |last= Barker |title= Film Review: ‘Peppermint’ |url= https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/peppermint-film-review-1202929343/ |website= Variety |accessdate= 2020-11-12 |archive-date= 2020-09-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200907063553/https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/peppermint-film-review-1202929343/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”《[[纽约_(杂志)|纽约]]》杂志的艾蜜丽·吉田（Emily Yoshida）表示，“有那么一段时间，出演糟糕的系列动作片的女明星被认为是进步的最高点，但现在这已经是过去式了”。她批评影片缺乏原创性，即使选嘉纳拍摄也没能改变这一点<ref name="Yoshida">{{cite web | date = 2018-09-07 | first = Emily | last = Yoshida | title = Peppermint is Bad, Old-Fashioned Action Schlock — and a Female Lead Doesn’t Change That | url = https://www.vulture.com/2018/09/peppermint-review.html | website = Vulture | accessdate = 2020-11-12 | archive-date = 2019-12-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191214214637/https://www.vulture.com/2018/09/peppermint-review.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

